xf86-video-sunxifb - video driver for devices based on the Allwinner A10/A13 SoC,
and other ARM-based devices.

Please submit bugs & patches to:

        https://github.com/ssvb/xf86-video-sunxifb

All questions regarding this software should be directed at the
linux-sunxi mailing list:

        https://groups.google.com/d/forum/linux-sunxi

This driver is intended to be a drop-in replacement for x86-video-mali
and the installation instructions from http://linux-sunxi.org should
also work. Gentoo Linux users may find the following portage overlay
useful to simplify the installation process:

        https://github.com/ssvb/gentoo-overlay-sunxi-x11
